    dc:creator "Schnabel, Kareen E.; Martin, Joel W.; Moffitt, Robert B." ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Additions to the decapod crustacean fauna of the Hawaiian Islands, III. A new species of the genus Babamunida (Crustacea: Galatheidae) from Hawaii based on morphological and molecular evidence" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188359>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188360> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188359>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Babamunida kanaloa n. sp. as observed (video frame) during a dive of the DSV Pisces IV off Penguin Banks (southwest of Molokai), 20 ° 58.536´N, 157 ° 22.731´W, 224 m, November 2006. Arrows denote live specimens. Note distinctive colour banding on the chelipeds." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188359/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188360>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. A, Maximum parsimony tree based on 16 S rRNA gene sequences. B, Maximum parsimony tree based on CO 1 mtDNA gene sequences. Numbers indicate bootstrap values (1000 replicates)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188360/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

